System
  Display system info
    inxi - Fxz
    lshw
    lscpu
  Storage
    lsblk

Networking
    nmcli
  IP
    ip addr ~ show ip address
  DNS
    nslookup <domain name>
    dig <domain name>
    systemd-resolve --status
USERS
adduser ~ interactive add user account
usermod -aG groupname user ~ adds 'user' to the 'groupname' group

DNS
sudo systemd-resolve --flush-cache
sudo systemd-resolve --statistics

